    videoScene: "<h4>🎬 Video Scene Description</h4><p>Three university students — David, Fatima, and Grace — are sitting at a round table in a campus library study room. Books and tablets are spread across the table. A whiteboard behind them shows 'Group Project: Urban Sustainability Report — Due April 18.' David has a pen in hand, doodling on his notepad. Fatima is looking at her laptop screen. Grace is flipping through a printed article.</p>",
